    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Thickly-Veiled Promises",
        "Description": "Both are pairs, when viewed in isolation. Yet, the pairs are linked in a way that half of them do not realise. Even when it is time for them to meet, they fail to see the unsavoury truth, tucked away behind a corner. Perhaps it is because the other other-half hides behind that mask, as extravagant or as dark these masks may be.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as linux_penguin.",
